title: Jack Ross (musician)
text:
Jack Ross (November 1, 1916 – December 16, 1982) was a popular rock and roll musician contemporary with Elvis Presley.


== Discography ==
"Cinderella" 1962
"Margarita", B-side "Milwaukee Stomp" 1962
"Happy Jose [Ching Ching]", B-side "Sweet Georgia Brown"
